    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 4. Selenops aztecus new species. Male (Holotype). 1 Habitus, dorsal view; 2 Left chelicera, teeth of promargin and retromargin view; 3 Left palp, ventral view; 4 Left palp, retrolateral view. Scales = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/275496/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

